Package net.sf.jguiraffe.gui.builder.components.tags

Interface IconSupport

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractActionDataTag, ActionControlTag, ActionDataTag, ActionTag, ButtonTag, CheckboxTag, DialogTag, FrameTag, InternalFrameTag, LabelTag, MenuItemTag, MenuTag, PushButtonTag, RadioButtonTag, StaticTextTag, TabTag, TextIconTag, ToggleButtonTag, ToolButtonTag, TreeIconTag, WindowBaseTag
    public interface IconSupport

    Definition of an interface for GUI components that support icons.

    This interface defines a single setter method for an icon object. This method is intended to be called by an IconTag, which loads an icon and sets it on the component it is nested inside.
